Revenue Intelligence for Financial Services:

Get predictions about customers who are likely to churn and reduce their likelihood by analyzing their churn scores. Identify Wealth Management customers likely to add more assets, pursue such customers with products for sale.

Churn Prediction for Retail Banking Customers:
Get predictions about Retail Management customers who are likely to churn.
Churn Prediction for Wealth Management Customers:
Get predictions about Wealth Management customers who are likely to churn.

Increase Your Assets Under Management from Wealth Management Customers:
Identify wealth management customers likely to add more assets, pursue such customers with products for sale.

Maximize Your Revenue by Recommending the Right Products to Customers:
Get predictions about recommended products that can be pitched to customers who are likely to buy them.

Scoring Framework Predictions:
Pitch the right products to customers and boost revenue by analyzing customer likelihood of purchasing financial assets.
Decrease customer attrition by taking steps based on customer likelihood of churning. Sell an asset to an interested customer based on predictions and increase customer's assets under management.

Required Editions: Available in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions with the Revenue Intelligence for Financial Services license.
